ip business / LLP / Private / Public Limited company. All those companies who are involved in manufacturing, trade, service sector enterprises, MSMEs would be eligible. Furthermore, applicant firm must not be a loan defaulter.Education LoanStudents residing in Haryana who have availed the education loan after January 1 2015, the loan interest for all such students charged from the month of April 2020 to June 2020, would be borne by the state government. The Education loan application form will appear as shown below at the Atmanirbhar Haryana portal:-Education Loan Waiver Registration Atmanirbhar Haryana PortalThe main objective of this Atmanirbhar Haryana Scheme is to make the process of taking and repaying loans hassle-free in order to make poor and needy people self-reliant. At the same time, it will also help in strengthening the Haryana economy after the COVID-19 lockdown.Apply Online to Book Your Bank SlotPeople can now also book their bank slot online for cash deposit or withdrawal at the Atmanirbhar Haryana Portal. For this purpose, applicants can click at the \u201c\u092c\u0941\u0915 \u092c\u0948\u0902\u0915 \u0938\u094d\u0932\u0949\u091f\u201d tab present in the main menu or at or \u201c\u0906\u091c \u0939\u0940 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u093e \u092c\u0948\u0902\u0915 \u0938\u094d\u0932\u0949\u091f \u0926\u0930\u094d\u091c \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902 (\u092f\u0939\u093e\u0901 \u0915\u094d\u0932\u093f\u0915 \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902)\u201d link on the homepage of Atmanirbhar Haryana portal or directly click this link. Then the apply bank slot page will appear as shown below:-Book Bank Slot Atmanirbhar Haryana Gov PortalAt this page, applicants can enter their name, mobile number, IFSC code, date, available slot and click at the \u201cApply Slot\u201d tab.Access Postal Banking ServicesPeople can access postal banking services postal banking services through the link below:- https://atmanirbhar.haryana.gov.in/frontend/web/index.php/registration/postalThe page to apply for postal bank service at Atmanirbhar Haryana Portal will appear as shown below:-Apply Postal Bank Service Atmanirbhar Haryana PortalHere applicants will have to enter name, mobile no., amount, district, city, pincode, address and click at the \u201cApply\u201d button to apply for postal banking services at Atmanirbhar Haryana portal.Earlier PM Modi had announced Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan economic package of Rs. 20 lakh crore. Haryana gets the benefit of at-least 10% of this package and govt. will now take care of every person residing in the state. Special teams have been formed for this task by the Haryana government, which is working on all aspects. A system is being prepared by the government for this task and Parivar Pehchan Patra of all the families are being made so that information of every member of each family can be collected and every needy person can be ensured the benefit of government schemes.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://atmanirbhar.haryana.gov.in/frontend/web/  at  "}